Package: rteachtools
Title: Tools For Teaching
Version: 0.0.7
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Peter",
           family = "von Rohr",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "peter.vonrohr@gmail.com")
Description: Teaching courses requires to create, manage, distribute and publish 
    a lot of material for the students. Nowadays the publication and the distribution 
    is done via the web. This package contains a set of tools that fascilitates the 
    management of the material needed in a course.
